quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,94,"“Ndipo musakuchite kulumbira kwanu kukhala njira yonyengelerana pakati panu, kuopera kuti mwendo ungatelere (pa njira yolungama nkukagwera ku Moto) pambuyo pokhazikika mwendowo (pa njirapo) ndi kukazilawa zoipa chifukwa chakutsekereza kwanu (anthu) ku njira ya Allah, ndipo nkupeza chilango chachikulu (tsiku lachimaliziro)"
  16,95,"“Ndipo musagulitse mapangano a Allah ndi mtengo wochepa (wa zomwe mukupeza pano pa dziko lapansi). Chimene chili kwa Allah, ndicho chabwino kwa inu ngati mukudziwa"
  16,96,“Zomwe mulinazo nzakutha ndipo zili kwa Allah ndizo zosatha. Ndithudi Ife tidzawapatsa malipiro (aakulu zedi) amene adapirira oposera zabwino zimene ankachita
  16,97,"“Amene akuchita zabwino, wamwamuna kapena wamkazi uku ali wokhulupirira timkhazika ndi moyo wabwino (pano pa dziko, ndi tsiku la Qiyâma) tidzawalipira malipiro awo mochuluka kwambiri chifukwa cha zabwino zomwe ankachita"
  16,98,“Ndipo ukafuna kuwerenga Qur’an dzitchinjirize ndi Allah kwa satana wopirikitsidwa (ponena kuti Awudhu Billahi mina Shaitwani Rajim)
  16,99,“Ndithu iye (satana) alibe mphamvu pa amene akhulupirira ndi kutsamira kwa Mbuye wawo
  16,100,“Ndithudi mphamvu zake zili pa amene akumusankha (amulola) kukhala bwenzi lawo (mlangizi wawo) ndiponso ndi omwe akumphatikiza iye (ndi Allah)
  16,101,"“Ndipo tikasintha Ayah (ndime) ndikubwera ndi Ina pamalopo, pomwe Allah akudziwa zimene akuvumbulutsa, akunena: “Ndithu iwe ndiwe wopeka.” Koma ambiri a iwo sadziwa (chilichonse)"
  16,102,"“Nena: “Mzimu woyera (Gabriel) waitsitsa (Qur’an) kuchokera kwa Mbuye wako mwachoonadi kuti awalimbikitse nayo amene akhulupirira ndi kuti ikhale chiongoko ndi nkhani yabwino kwa amene alowa m’Chisilamu (amene agonjera Allah)"